Starting: java -jar pipesilters.jar (when in same directory)
Program arguments:  -overwrite (output file is overwritten when exists)
                    -line=100 (desired length of lines for task b, minimum of longest uninterrupted (no whitespaces) string + 1)
                    -alignment=CENTER (desired alignment of text; allowed values: LEFT, CENTER, RIGHT)
                    a (execute pipeline from task a -> only index)
                    b (execute pipelines from task b -> index and aligned text)
